Tampa Northern Railroad Company, Plaintiff in Error, v. Hugh Hale, et al., Defendants in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Hernando. Knight, Thompson & Tv/rner and Geo. 0. Martin, for Plaintiff in Error; FredI L. Stringer and Hugh Hale, for Defendants in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for Plaintiff in Error.
